title: Model Squad
overview: Supermodels nowadays don't just walk the catwalk; they're everywhere and, of course, they're staples of the New York nightlife and fashion scenes. When you're the hottest women in pop culture, you travel in packs. This series follows a group of supermodel friends as they explore work, life and love in the Big Apple together. The cast features Olivia Culpo, Devon Windsor, Shanina Shaik, Hannah Ferguson, Nadine Leopold, Caroline Lowe, Daniela Braga, Ashley Moore and Ping Hue. "Model Squad" is produced by Trooper Entertainment.
